OL,3,CRomford man's 5000 mile walk Ghana to
OL,4,Cscatter his fiancee's ashes at her home
OL,6,FDaniel Forrester from Romford is
OL,7,Fwalking 5 thousand miles to take his
OL,8,Fashes home, he spoke to Jay Akbar
OL,9,Fabout love, loss - and keeping his word
OL,11,FWords by Jay Akbar and Rachel Dixon
OL,13,FWhen Daniel Forrester's fiancee
OL,14,FCaroline was dying he promised that he
OL,15,Fwould walk her home one last time.
OL,17,FBut that journey, to scatter her
OL,18,Fashes, is more than five thousand
OL,19,Fmiles long, because Caroline grew up
OL,20,Fin Ghana.
