OL,3,CRomford man's 5000 mile walk Ghana to
OL,4,Cscatter his fiancee's ashes at her home
OL,6,FHe left Romford 70 days ago and is
OL,7,Fmaking his way through Spain to the
OL,8,Fnorth of Africa.
OL,10,FMr Forrester told ITV News London: "I
OL,11,Fwanted Caroline's life to keep giving
OL,12,Fafter her life has finished.
OL,14,F"She gave me so much I want to give
OL,15,Fsomething back"
OL,17,FHe's also doing the walk to raise
OL,18,Ffunds for Saint Francis Hospice, in
OL,19,FRomford, where Caroline passed in 2024.
OL,26,@lD@RrrwD@OO]
