OL,3,CRomford man's 5000 mile walk Ghana to
OL,4,Cscatter his fiancee's ashes at her home
OL,6,F"With St Francis Hospice their ethos
OL,7,Fis care and we felt care, not only for
OL,8,FCaroline but for her family and myself
OL,9,Fas well." he said.
OL,11,FHe set off from there a year late and
OL,12,Fhas been walking all day ever since.
OL,14,FWhile it's been mentally and
OL,15,Fphysically exhausting, having Caroline
OL,16,Fconstantly on his mind keeps him going.
OL,18,FMr Forrester said: "If I was doing
OL,19,Fthis for me, I would've quit eight
OL,20,Fweeks ago, easily."
