OL,3,CRomford man's 5000 mile walk Ghana to
OL,4,Cscatter his fiancee's ashes at her home
OL,6,F"There's been weeks where I've done
OL,7,Ffive or six marathons in a week.
OL,9,F"The first week I did 166 miles. I was
OL,10,Fgetting injured. I had blisters the
OL,11,Fsize of Jaffa Cakes.
OL,13,F"I thought I broke my ankle. The
OL,14,Fadrenaline got the better of me."
OL,16,FThe hospice are following Mr
OL,17,FForrester's every step, through his
OL,18,Fdaily posts on Facebook and TikTok.
