OL,3,CRomford man's 5000 mile walk Ghana to
OL,4,Cscatter his fiancee's ashes at her home
OL,6,FHead of Public Fundraising at the
OL,7,Fhospice, Ryan O'Connor, said: "It's
OL,8,Fnot only the funds he's going to raise
OL,9,Fbut its the awareness of hospice care,
OL,10,Fwhat it provides for communities and
OL,11,Fhow important it is.
OL,13,F"If he can shed light on that then its
OL,14,Fa fantastic thing in itself."
OL,16,FAs to what Caroline would have thought
OL,17,Fof his mission, Daniel joked that she
OL,18,Fwould not have been impressed.
